step_data.thought: I've successfully applied a filter to show orders with Grand Total (Base) greater than or equal to $200. However, I notice there's also a date filter applied (Purchase Date: 3/01/2022 - 3/31/2022) which might be restricting our results. To find ALL orders with a total value greater than $200, regardless of date, I should remove this date filter. I can do this by clicking the 'x' button next to the date filter.
